How to start:
    - Make sure you have nodejs v16^ installed in your system.
    - Make sure you have expo installed. https://docs.expo.dev/get-started/installation/
    - Make sure you have expo installed on your phone. https://apps.apple.com/us/app/expo-go/id982107779
      P.S. The app was initially developed for iphone, be aware of issues when if you try android.
    - To Install all dependencies: "npm install"
    - To Run Application run: "npm start"
    - After an application booted up, open your iphone, open your camera and look at the QRCode in your console, this will redirect to
      expo app on your phone and start an application on your phone which you can interact with.
